<emphasis bold="true" box="[475,566,1859,1885]" pageId="3" pageNumber="454">
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[475,566,1859,1885]" pageId="3" pageNumber="454" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
is very distinctive among the species of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Viraktamath &amp; Webb &amp; Yeshwanth" authorityYear="2021" box="[1032,1150,1858,1884]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Yelahanka" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="454" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
